Package: ABitBored
Title: Kill the time with some fun games
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Siard", "Groot",
                  email = "siard@example.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A collection of a few interactive FUNctions which
    are playable in the R console. The package includes blackjack, a slotmachine,
    two player tic tac toe and a magic R ball. Enjoy these games if you find
    yourself with some spare time.
